conditional statements = used to make decisions in code (such as true and false)
control flow = determines which code runs based off of condiions

- if statement = only runs if condition is true
- if...else = two outcomes
-   if condition = true (run first block)
- else= run second block

else if = checks multiple conditions
evaluated top 

Comparison Operators
>, <, >=, <=, ==, ===

Logical Operators
&& = AND
|| = OR
! = NOT

Boolean values = conditions to evaluate if true or false

